markdown : '''
* SQL is the programming language for talking to databases

* We haven't had to use SQL because we've just been using Django ORM

* The definition of ORM: code that writes SQL for you

* On most "well-run" web projects, if you are in a typical Jr Backend or Full
  Stack Dev position, ~95% of the time you will be using ORM only to interact
  the database

* Only ~5% of the time you will need to use SQL

